{"id": "1271059191271784489", "channel_id": "1271059191271784489", "type": 0, "author_id": "1122207553053528217", "author_name": "yi000607", "author_bot": false, "content": "遊玩143天\n第一次打到375分享給需要的朋朋\n順序從5-4打到1-4。\n5-4：超維24\n4-4：神父環拉\n3-4：尤烏羊媽\n2-4：鯊魚水母\n1-4：深海毒\n總共是2深海2血肉1超維\n\n5-4\n超維24好用得點在於道中可以過得非常舒服，但以這次Boss為N的情況，其實混沌24回更合適，不過我的環拉已經配給神父了所以也沒辦法\n4-4\n一階段羅坦的攻擊力非常低，就用蜘蛛慢慢疊戒備+神父慢慢磨，在一階段打命定的傷害撐起來，2階段我雙命定一回合斬殺，就算不能斬殺也能靠菲神死抗硬扛。\n3-4\n尤烏一定是能扛一關沒啥好說，不過我的練度很低，因此造物算是很好的情況下才順利過，有超限尤烏會更輕鬆\n2-4 1-4\n慢慢磨即可，我是有凹死抗才過，畢竟練度超低\n也能用深海盾或者利茲毒、希落打擊去打\nUID:100394120", "timestamp": "2024-08-08T10:55:26.337000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-08-08T10:59:01.420000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "♥️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1271059191670247494", "filename": "Screenshot_20240808_185449.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 103360, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271059191271784489/1271059191670247494/Screenshot_20240808_185449.jpg?ex=69fb1e1e&is=69f9cc9e&hm=fccbce39f83f5b552d412a387978c034686b8a32a5f721b82b9c263e94703f0b&"}, {"id": "1271059192114970695", "filename": "Screenshot_20240808_185452.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 102100, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271059191271784489/1271059192114970695/Screenshot_20240808_185452.jpg?ex=69fb1e1e&is=69f9cc9e&hm=ef66c73f84046e7e3546254cd143e332682b96a3e9d1585a51c16d388dfa0009&"}, {"id": "1271059192408707082", "filename": "Screenshot_20240808_185444.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 140760, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271059191271784489/1271059192408707082/Screenshot_20240808_185444.jpg?ex=69fb1e1e&is=69f9cc9e&hm=18723b29f1b7627b6cf44c91be4ff3c885d51917fa5ca6e93ba9719d69b56737&"}, {"id": "1271059192718950410", "filename": "Screenshot_20240808_185435.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 144019, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271059191271784489/1271059192718950410/Screenshot_20240808_185435.jpg?ex=69fb1e1e&is=69f9cc9e&hm=5652de2a5349c4ba9af0d585a97d7d99f25e0baed5633f32b36f8c09a5180fe8&"}, {"id": "1271059192953700403", "filename": "Screenshot_20240808_185429.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 143233, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271059191271784489/1271059192953700403/Screenshot_20240808_185429.jpg?ex=69fb1e1e&is=69f9cc9e&hm=e26d21a3651ef97fcb543089d0bac4123b230a89d7836f09c05b519774eae016&"}, {"id": "1271059193264083045", "filename": "Screenshot_20240808_185423.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 142280, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271059191271784489/1271059193264083045/Screenshot_20240808_185423.jpg?ex=69fb1e1e&is=69f9cc9e&hm=75369002c900ff5430b1650be6f68106ba013140740343a150f963c18b51d6ec&"}, {"id": "1271059193654411344", "filename": "Screenshot_20240808_185418.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 141672, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271059191271784489/1271059193654411344/Screenshot_20240808_185418.jpg?ex=69fb1e1e&is=69f9cc9e&hm=d583ebc7de52b63247f6d1326743f799e65f7ec723db72c50825f793134fa0bf&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1271059191271784489", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超低練度溶災375攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1260133992636743681", "1181143392739147778", "1174179680056791130"]}
{"id": "1271052437394030684", "channel_id": "1271052437394030684", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "本期打了純超維的融災375，~~都打了就想來曬一下~~，並提供一些超維在融災配對的思路和強度建議。\n\n首先我會盡量抓一個銀鑰位，一個生存位，並圍繞著主C的打法選擇配合的角色。\n\n而詩人在超維界域是非常強非常關鍵的角色，有了詩人的超維隊伍強度上升不只一個檔次，因此助戰借詩人。\n\n不過我在關卡選擇上出了些問題，導致打得比較艱難，換一下順序會好打很多，留言是詳細陣容。\n\n2024.8.8.mob\n\nUID:100352106", "timestamp": "2024-08-08T10:28:36.087000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-08-08T10:34:37.751000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [{"id": "1271052437691568128", "filename": "375_1.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 165699, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271052437394030684/1271052437691568128/375_1.JPG?ex=69fb17d4&is=69f9c654&hm=0d29955e7327ca8df0bcc3855e19bf05fda779052cc2b1fb94029d190207ddca&"}, {"id": "1271052438106935328", "filename": "375_2.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 166772, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1271052437394030684/1271052438106935328/375_2.JPG?ex=69fb17d4&is=69f9c654&hm=c4fc44557617c7088022024041655e582b8f7fb4bfa95c9888e094062ede07b7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1271052437394030684", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "超維融災375", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778", "1174179755759763526"]}
